{"type":"question","id":10697,"title":"如何评价中科院外籍员工Kolars关于中国人的言论？","uid":3685,"topics":[408,503,4,1502],"contents":"据推特@williamlong&nbsp;<br>\n【中科院不当言论外籍员工被限期离境】近日，中国科学院自动化研究所聘雇人员奥地利籍男子Mark A.Kolars，在社交平台发表不当言论，引发公众关注。11月7日，中国科学院自动化研究所已与Mark A.Kolars解除工作合同。当日，北京市公安局出入境管理局注销Mark A.Kolars所持的工作类居留许可、限期离境。<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EInCAo8UwAAVTB_?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EInCAo8UwAAVTB_?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EInCAo8UwAAVTB_?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EInCBIGUUAIRDMV?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EInCBIGUUAIRDMV?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EInCBIGUUAIRDMV?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EInCBSMVAAADLCa?format=jpg&amp;name=360x360\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EInCBSMVAAADLCa?format=jpg&amp;name=360x360\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EInCBSMVAAADLCa?format=jpg&amp;name=360x360\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EInCBniUEAAgdjz?format=jpg&amp;name=360x360\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EInCBniUEAAgdjz?format=jpg&amp;name=360x360\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EInCBniUEAAgdjz?format=jpg&amp;name=360x360\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-11-08","agreeCount":2,"discussionCount":0}